## Data Validation Best Practices

When working with analytics data:

```javascript
import { validateDataIntegrity } from './utils/dataValidation';

const result = validateDataIntegrity(rawData);
if (!result.valid) {
  console.error('Data validation failed:', result.errors);
  // Handle errors - show ErrorState
}
```

**Required fields for analytics data:**
- MONTH (format: YYYY-MM)
- SIGNUPS, APPLICANTS, ACCEPTED, REJECTED, WAITLISTED, REGISTERED (numeric strings)

