## Quick Reference

**New Frontend Project:**
```bash
npm create vite@latest project-name -- --template react
cd project-name
npm install
npm run dev
```

**New Backend Project:**
```bash
mkdir backend
cd backend
npm init -y
npm install express cors dotenv
npm install -D typescript @types/express @types/node ts-node-dev
npx tsc --init
```

**Add to Docker:**
1. Ensure Dockerfile.vite exists in root
2. Add service to docker-compose.yml
3. Run: `docker-compose build <service-name>`
4. Run: `docker-compose up <service-name>`

**Add to CI/CD:**
1. Add step to bitbucket-pipelines.yml
2. Define changesets for the project directory
3. Push to trigger build
